<h3>Text inputs and textareas</h3>
<p>Notes on help text:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Inline</strong> - Only use the inline style to denote that a field is required.</li>
    <li><strong>Help</strong> - Use the help style to give context or directions for a particular field, like a character count.</li>
    <li><strong>Placeholder</strong> - Use placeholder text to give an actual example of what you might write (do not include additional text, such as "ex:" or "e.g.").</li>
</ul>



